          oa:exact "the problem becomes that theme is interpretive - ie claims can be read different ways, and reducing a claim to a single theme is exactly the kind of reductionism" ;
          oa:prefix "On the proposal to give each node a coverage signature, Scarlet identified the trap: " ;
          oa:suffix " that steering and statements about statements attempts to avoid."
        ]
